item.title: CVE-2019-5266|2024-08-04T19:47:56.820Z -- huawei -- share%20function%20p30
item.description: Huawei Share function in P30 9.1.0.193(C00E190R2P1) smartphone has an insufficient input validation vulnerability. Attackers can exploit this vulnerability by sending crafted packets to the affected device. Successful exploit may cause the function will be disabled.
